  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    The Controller class is used to test various CRUD methods belonging to the EmployeeDAO class.
    ControllerGUI
    The ControllerGUI class is used to display the MainForm's GUI in order for the user to interact with and use the database.
    Employee
    Employee is a base class containing attributes typically belonging to an organisation's employee.
    EmployeeDAO
    EmployeeDAO provides a connection to the empdb.sqlite database along with CRUD methods in order to perform various operations upon the database records.
    MainForm
    The MainForm displays an interface providing various features to the user wishing to access the database.
    Person
    Person is a base class containing attributes typically belonging to a person.
    SearchForm
    The SearchForm is used to help the user retrieve record(s) that they specifically want to see.
